Europe Must Stop Italy, Spain Crisis Contagion, Urpilainen Says

-- B y   K a t i   P o h j a n p a l o
-- 
2011-10-05T18:51:29Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-05/europe-must-stop-italy-spain-crisis-contagion-urpilainen-says.html
European countries must do everything
they can to stop contagion of the sovereign debt crisis into
Italy and  Spain , Finnish Finance Minister Jutta Urpilainen said
in a television interview on YLE TV1 today.  Italy and Spain are in a key position to stop contagion,
she said. A “sustainable” solution for  Greece  would help stem
the crisis, she said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Kati Pohjanpalo at 
 kpohjanpalo@bloomberg.net  